Filter(LANG(?country_name)='it') Filter(LANG(?locality_name)='it') Filter regex(str(?geo_names), '^http://sws.geonames.org/.*$')}Filter(?main_place = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferrara>)}UNION{?place geo:lat ?lat .?place geo:long ?long . OPTIONAL { ?place rdfs:label ?locality_name . ?place dbpedia-owl:country ?country . ?country rdfs:label ?country_name . ?place owl:sameAs ?geo_names . ?place dbpedia-owl:postalCode ?postal_code . Filter(LANG(?country_name)='it') Filter(LANG(?locality_name)='it') Filter regex(str(?geo_names), '^http://sws.geonames.org/.*$')}Filter(?place = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferrara>)}}LIMIT 1	
PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT * WHERE { {?city rdfs:label 'Probolinggo'@en.} UNION { ?alias <http://dbpedia.org/property/redirect> ?city; rdfs:label 'Probolinggo'@en. } UNION { ?alias <http://dbpedia.org/property/disambiguates> ?city; rdfs:label 'Probolinggo'@en. } OPTIONAL { ?city <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/abstract> ?abstract} OPTIONAL { ?city geo:lat ?latitude; geo:long ?longitude} OPTIONAL { ?city foaf:depiction ?image } OPTIONAL { ?city rdfs:label ?name } OPTIONAL { ?city foaf:homepage ?home } OPTIONAL { ?city <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/populationTotal> ?population } OPTIONAL { ?city <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/thumbnail> ?thumbnail } FILTER (langMatches( lang(?abstract), 'en'))}

OPTIONAL { dbpedia:Cardiac_muscle foaf:depiction ?image . } FILTER (LANG(?abstract)='en' && LANG(?comment)='en') }

PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX ontology: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> select distinct ?person ?deathDate ?dbpedia ?wikipedia ?depiction ?comment ?thumbnail where { ?dbpedia rdfs:label ?person; rdf:type ontology:Person. ?dbpedia ontology:deathDate ?deathDate FILTER ( ?deathDate > \"1898-01-01\"^^xsd:date). OPTIONAL {?dbpedia foaf:isPrimaryTopicOf ?wikipedia. } OPTIONAL {?dbpedia foaf:depiction ?depiction. } ?dbpedia rdfs:comment ?comment. FILTER ( lang(?person ) = 'en' ) FILTER ( lang(?comment ) = 'en' ). } limit 10
